      <title>匈牙利对奥尔班反腐行动中的反腐监督机构展开调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/hungary-launches-probe-against-graft-watchdog-in-orban-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班设立的备受争议的国家机构已开始对反腐监督机构透明国际的匈牙利分支机构展开调查，这是其针对批评匈牙利政权的民间团体的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/hungary-launches-probe-against-graft-watchdog-in-orban-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 14:40:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登与特朗普的对决对美国股市意味着什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/biden-trump-rematch-what-it-means-for-us-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年，墨西哥、印度和欧洲的选举引发了全球股市的动荡。在美国，投资者正努力应对与通胀、利率和地缘政治相关的不确定性，他们已经为可能伴随总统竞选和 11 月大选而来的波动做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/biden-trump-rematch-what-it-means-for-us-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 14:05:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士总统称，瑞士力争今年与欧盟达成新协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/switzerland-aims-to-secure-new-eu-deal-this-year-president-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士希望今年完成与欧盟的新协议谈判，为这个多年来屡遭阻碍的长期问题制定时间表。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/switzerland-aims-to-secure-new-eu-deal-this-year-president-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 13:37:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>托兹称拜登胜选可能比特朗普更扰乱市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/biden-win-could-disrupt-markets-more-than-trump-tooze-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经济历史学家亚当·图兹表示，即使乔·拜登赢得第二任期，美国严重的党派分歧也可能给市场带来不确定性。这是因为如果他再次击败唐纳德·特朗普，共和党人可能会更加猛烈地抨击他。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/biden-win-could-disrupt-markets-more-than-trump-tooze-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 12:45:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲法院裁定俄罗斯在克里米亚虐待乌克兰人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/russia-tortured-ukrainians-in-crimea-human-rights-court-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲人权法院裁定，自 2014 年占领克里米亚以来，俄罗斯对乌克兰公民实施了酷刑、殴打和其他多项侵犯人权的行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/russia-tortured-ukrainians-in-crimea-human-rights-court-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 11:04:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“这改变了一切”：特鲁多因失去多伦多席位而受到打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/canada-s-conservatives-win-liberal-stronghold-in-blow-to-trudeau</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大保守党赢得多伦多市中心一个选区的特别选举，这对总理贾斯汀·特鲁多领导的自由党在明年全国选举前造成了重大打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/canada-s-conservatives-win-liberal-stronghold-in-blow-to-trudeau</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 10:59:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
